articles.title: SMOKED: Nebraska Football Rolled by Curt Cignetti’s Indiana Hoosiers, 56-7 - Sports Illustrated
articles.description: Nebraska football was dominated from start to finish Saturday in Bloomington, falling to No. 16 Indiana, 56-7.
articles.content:
Nebraska football was supposed to be the toughest opponent Indiana had faced all season. Instead, the Huskers were just another opponent to get rolled by the Hoosiers.
